---
title: Speedy Beef Stroganoff with Fusilli
description: Our take on this classic Russian recipe is a speedy ground beef dinner the whole family will fall in love with. The tangy, creamy sauce pairs beautifully with buttery pasta!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/boeufstroganoff-10b9884a.jpg
